➜有哪些明知是智商税的坑，让你边骂边喊真香的？
http://www.sohu.com/a/413692289_425113	25342
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/0a09141f57e74a9d82faafb78bcd2db9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/dbbb181563114ff88622d795a263fbb5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每日好似苦行僧，唯有暴富最轻松</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为一只社畜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总是幻想着有一天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">啥都不干就能躺在床上数钱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是乎他们几乎不放过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">任何有可能暴富的机会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哪里火热，哪里入坑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果却总是被当成韭菜收割</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/47239bb6dd8f47df9ecc38124927738f.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">小韭菜的心酸血泪史</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闻者伤心听者流泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但话说回来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>「韭菜」这个词到底是怎么来的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为什么每次被割的都是它</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而不是包菜、白菜、空心菜呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/f861b3db9fac40a9bbbfa40f2ccf27ca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">「割韭菜」的概念</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最早源自<strong>股票交易市场</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而「韭菜」指的就是那些</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒霉催的散户</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们一买就套，一套就割，一割就涨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一涨就追，一追再套</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本来喜滋滋地做着以小博大的发财梦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醒来钱却都进了别人的口袋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/23223b3f9cbe4c81869b9f9309d8620b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更加悲惨的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们还总是不长记性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在被收割了后仍然对股市充满希望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坚信没到最后<strong>谁都不是loser</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后一次又一次地投钱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一点跟「韭菜」这种植物的特点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刚好不谋而合</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">韭菜是蔬菜中颜色不一样的烟火</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生长速度快不说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一长就是密密麻麻的一大片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且它还有个「<strong>特异功能</strong>」</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被割掉一截后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没过多久马上又可以长到原来那么高</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不像包菜、白菜、空心菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被割了一次之后菜心就烂了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以「韭菜」被割了一茬后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很快又可以再割一茬，源源不尽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跟这些好了伤疤忘了疼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总是被忽悠着花冤枉钱的“小散户”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简直一毛一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/894744e380604c1b8ac0cd5c4559c757.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后来「韭菜」一词渐渐火出了圈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长到了币圈、知识付费圈等新土地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>于是现在凡是花了冤枉钱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>交了智商税的行为</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都可以称为「割韭菜」</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/0448186413c1450098a7f2f0b8c0e99f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">「韭菜」入圈无非是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抱着赌徒的心态<strong>想走捷径</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以当同龄人都在脚踏实地努力的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们却在碰运气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总是满怀壮志地进场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却不知自己将头抬得高高的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好方便了镰刀收割</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/13d922c729a64aee8d4d58df76491f3b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在我们就来看看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小韭菜们都在哪些坑里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心甘情愿地被割吧~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/cfaa3f7170c4453ea10aa745b8702a94.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/5bdd029711d6409dba013e8b11ec8c47.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/c2a8b367936842fc8abb8d808e63f984.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/13e079932a024603b0719748105609b1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/24fd8075a6da40e9a363ea09dabd8be8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/847e1fa724b04bbb960aafa0c90c8ac4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/032a85d350c74b79913190da8a0a0981.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怀着一颗走捷径的心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果却只有被割韭菜的命</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么如何才能摆脱这种悲惨的命运呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/d29a8b0074994af89e649671efd0c634.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有个成语叫做：<strong>利令智昏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用来形容想花小钱占大便宜的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再合适不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在被各种夸大宣传的好处面前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不能保持冷静的思考</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就容易掉入陷阱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/9579e4c79dda4287b29b8a559f0f40c9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每次看到别人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赚钱了、变美了、瘦身成功了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就总是急着入场分一杯羹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以为机会是留给手快的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却没有看到它背后潜藏的风险</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/81842903d76b426a842552b51cf83d55.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有时甚至明知道里面有猫腻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还忍不住放胆一试</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟说不定自己是镰刀呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们总认为自己很聪明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却不知道市场的水很深</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一代更比一代坑…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/90c8a4f062644747b0aed1ee6cb388ba.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明明没什么实力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又高估了自己的运气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每次入场都做着躺赢的美梦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到头来却总给别人当接盘侠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/df1206d1f187453385dada2fbc5719f1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以就算你觉得自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻身的机会不多了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在新风口面前也要<strong>保持清醒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明白这世界上没有天上掉馅饼的好事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也轮不到非洲人本非的你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（欧气爆棚的大佬请忽略）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样一来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">做决策的时候就会谨慎得多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/5f44df249d88457cb89a7dd1c3942944.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各种韭菜项目</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都喜欢披着高大上的外衣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扰乱大家的判断</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以更需要花时间和耐心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>去看清事物的本质和发展趋势</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">越是觉得「过了这个村就没这个店」</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">越要保持理智</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为它可能只是一种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逼你冲动消费的手段</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/12b32d1af8074583912ffe5ca3fd9c5b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以作为一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">手里没多少闲钱的社畜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想要暴富之前先得耳根子坚挺</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">了解各种花式割法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">列个负面清单</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样当生活的镰刀向你挥来的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才能知道躲闪啊！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/15c490fe6bc24bd19b57cce7d657d6f9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
